% 0.	Definitions
% I.	Nouns
% II.	Pronouns
% III.	Determiners
% IV.	Verbs
%		A. Normal Verbs
%		B. Intransitive Verbs
%		C. Compound Verbs
%		D. Auxiliary Verbs
%		E. Subordinating Verbs
%		F. Passive Verbs
